                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Et son allure maladroite",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Révélait qu'il était blessé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le lièvre, le long du fossé,\nS'en revenait d'un pied qui boite,\nEt son allure maladroite\nRévélait qu'il était blessé."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Tout fumant, le poil hérissé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "La bouche en sang, l'oreille droite,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Le lièvre, le long du fossé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "S'en revenait d'un pied qui boite.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout fumant, le poil hérissé,\nLa bouche en sang, l'oreille droite,\nLe lièvre, le long du fossé,\nS'en revenait d'un pied qui boite."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "— « Ah ! s'il pouvait être pansé !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Mais la pauvre bête est bien coite. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et quand j'arrivai le front moite,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Hélas ! il avait trépassé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Le lièvre, le long du fossé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— « Ah ! s'il pouvait être pansé !\nMais la pauvre bête est bien coite. »\nEt quand j'arrivai le front moite,\nHélas ! il avait trépassé,\nLe lièvre, le long du fossé."
        }
